1
00:00:06,170 --> 00:00:08,310
♪In this life, why not aim high?♪

2
00:00:08,310 --> 00:00:11,890
♪Achieve greatness at the moon palace
and leave a mark♪

3
00:00:12,060 --> 00:00:13,890
♪Or follow in the footsteps
of the ancients♪

4
00:00:13,890 --> 00:00:15,520
♪Composing poems by the winding streams♪

5
00:00:15,520 --> 00:00:17,720
♪Drinking wine to celebrate
the end of mundane affairs♪

6
00:00:17,720 --> 00:00:20,350
♪Sighing at this life,
not yet part of the Jianghu♪

7
00:00:20,350 --> 00:00:23,480
♪Haven't galloped horses
and felt the sweeping wind♪

8
00:00:23,520 --> 00:00:25,500
♪I seek consistency♪

9
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:29,310
♪How can I expect a clear moon
to lament mediocrity?♪

10
00:00:30,110 --> 00:00:32,620
[Episode 19]

11
00:00:34,680 --> 00:00:36,160
I have cultivated for a thousand years,

12
00:00:36,360 --> 00:00:37,480
knowing everything
from the past and present.

13
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,400
Yet I still can't

14
00:00:39,400 --> 00:00:40,960
compare to you.

15
00:00:44,040 --> 00:00:44,840
Before I came here,

16
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:46,640
I had a glimpse of the sky,

17
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:48,600
and noticed unusual phenomena
in the Demon Realm

18
00:00:49,120 --> 00:00:49,920
that the imperial star has changed,

19
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:50,960
fearing a great change will happen.

20
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:53,800
Thus, in fact,

21
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:54,800
I came here

22
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:56,880
to set things right

23
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:58,240
in the right direction.

24
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:01,800
But

25
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:03,360
you have astonishing poetic talent

26
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,000
and the ability to govern the world.

27
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:07,800
Only now do I understand
that those anomalies

28
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,160
were not chaos.

29
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:11,800
Perhaps your emergence

30
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:14,240
is following the laws of nature.

31
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,080
Well,

32
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:20,240
