and soul dissipation.

187
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:28,400
The malevolent energy of the Demon Realm

188
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,560
will burst forth.

189
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,280
This force

190
