is enough to destroy
the entire Linyuan City.

191
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,040
The city's common people
won't be spared.

192
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:37,320
By then, all Six Realms

193
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:39,920
will be affected.

194
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,480
I can never become a real Demon King.

195
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:43,960
After all, a king

196
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:46,120
has to devote himself to the people

197
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:48,160
even if he has to die for it.

198
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,040
Such a state

199
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:50,960
is beyond my reach.

200
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:53,800
I would never sacrifice my life

201
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:54,760
for the people of the Demon.

