222
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:25,880
♪Tiny lights illuminating
our dwelling place♪

223
00:12:25,970 --> 00:12:28,730
♪Welcoming all creations as guests♪

224
00:12:28,730 --> 00:12:31,890
