immortality and persistence♪

225
00:12:32,130 --> 00:12:34,490
♪We've lived madly in our time♪

226
00:12:34,710 --> 00:12:37,380
♪Don't fear making
the same mistakes again♪

227
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:38,810
